    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it is very sound, with the engine and transmission performing smoothly and all major systems functioning as intended. The exterior retains a nice shine, though you may find some minor rock chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster and common touchpoints. It represents a solid, reliable choice for anyone looking for a quality vehicle that has many miles of dependable service left to offer.",
